<h1>New Host Notification</h1>

<p>
  Dear <%= @organisation.contact_name %>,
</p>
<p>
  Your organisation <%= @organisation.name %> new host has been created in MOBEEAS, waiting for your approval.
  This user would like to apply for ADMIN level, which means that he or she will purchase new tokes and issue the company's tokens.
  He or she will be able to create new opportunities for the organisation.
  Here is your new host details in MOBEEAS:
<p>

<p>
  <strong>Name:</strong>
  <%= @user.org_user_profile.name %>
</p>

<p>
  <strong>Phone:</strong>
  <%= @user.org_user_profile.phone %>
</p>

<p>
  <strong>Email:</strong>
  <%= @user.email %>
</p>

<p>
  <strong>Position:</strong>
  <%= @user.org_user_profile.position %>
</p>

<p>
  If you approve <%= @user.org_user_profile.name %> to be the admin host of your organisation, please click the link below.
  Thank you.
</p>
<% @org_user = OrgUser.find_by(user_id: @user.id, organisation_id: @organisation.id) %>
<p>@org_user.organisation_id = <%= @org_user.organisation_id %></p>
<p>@org_user.user_id = <%= @org_user.user_id %></p>

<p><%= link_to 'Approve '+@user.org_user_profile.name, verified_and_admin_approved_org_user_url(@org_user.id, org_id: @organisation.id) %></p>
